title: GHOST
synopsis: Karan Khanna, a young politician in his 20s is quickly gaining foothold in London as the face of the youth, when all of sudden he finds himself behind bars for the murder of his wife Barkha Khanna. All the evidence is against him and no money or influence is able to get him lawyer to prove his innocence. Karan is convinced that his wifes death is not the work of a killer but the work of a spirit. At the last straw he seeks the counsel of Simran Singh, a young, vibrant, criminal lawyer who has already made her mark as one of the best lawyers in the United Kingdom and the crown court. Simran is hesitant to meet Karan but eventually she agrees to hear him out. Karan tries to explain her that he was innocent and it was a spirit that was behind everything. Simran doesnt believe him. However Simran is intrigued with case and strange things starts happening around him. Karan Simran begin to find themselves attracted to each other as they prepare for the battle of the paranormal against the judiciary. Simran starts find the clue about spirit and succeed to prove Karan is an innocence.

Kencha Sees Girl Ganga, Anand Also Likes Her And Both Gets Married, Anand Will Not Be Liking Swamy , Didt Giving Any Respect, People In Village Scolds Him For His Behaviour,Anand Tells He Is Fake Swamy That He Is Going To Reveal His True Colours, After Marriage, Swamy Comes And Puts Break For The First Night, That There Is Planets Problem That Both Should Not Sleep Till He Say, Anand Gets Very Angry. title: AFR1A
format: Doctor says vikram that his mother suffering from Brain Tumour and needs to be operated immediately. Vikram will request with everybody but unable to arrange fifty lakhs for his mothers operation. Vikram thinks that these all because of his father debt that he couldnt arrange money for the operation. Then his mother will explain everything about the property and loss because of that. Vikram and his friend go to that Bungalow which his father purchased and left. Through the village people he comes to know about that bungalow and that is scary ghost place so no one will dare to go there. At any cost vikram wanted to sell that bungalow and arrange for his mother operation. Buyer agrees to buy this bungalow on one condition to clear off superstitious beliefs. He tells them to live in that bungalow for a week then he will buy. Vikram will accept his condition and proceed on to live there. At the same time he will arrange one reality show in that bungalow. While going on this reality show they will come to know about the ghost. After knowing the difficulties of vikram all the contestants will agree to help him. They will arrange one swamiji to get rid off from the ghost then all they will come to know about Dhamayanti.Dhamayanti is the one and only daughter for Vijaya Rajendra Varma and for their province. The small and a happiest family use to help poor and they were famous for donations and services. Due to plague Dhamayanti mother will die so her father decides to construct one hospital so that no one can suffer and to live longer life. His wish is to serve people in such a way and wanted Dhamayanti become a doctor and help the poor. Bhaira is a criminal a far relative of Vijaya Rajendra Varma. title: TRAILER OF THE FILM - BABRU
synopsis: Babru Its a thrilling story that takes place between the two people. Sana she lost her daughter, Blamed by her husband, She plans to visit her sister who was abroad. Likewise the Hero of the movie Arjun plans to visit his girlfriend who was also in abroad. Both of them face a situation to rent the same car. On mutual understanding both Sana and Arjun started the journey by the same car. While travelling they started sharing their memories and purpose of their life. In that journey they came to know there were Drugs in the same car. In between a unknown person joins their journey Why the Unknown Person is behind Sana and Arjun What are the Changes in Life of Sana and Arjun Are they able to reach their goal is the story of Babru

title: ARUN UPANAL - BANGALORE URBAN
synopsis: The widowed mother, who gives birth to a baby boy and dies, the born blind baby, grows up under the auspices of a grandmother. Grandmother life is earned by earning a wage. That blind child, who harbors a grandmother for everything, fears many catastrophes and disasters during her developmental stages. The grandmother worried by this, was doing her best to make the baby look and give it to her grandson for medical attention. The grandmother who was been asked to register as an eye sight seeker in one of the citys well known eye hospital, learns that she has to pay a fixed fee to register her grandsons name. The old woman who has collected from her earnings is not enough a blind man who knows her problems donates as much he can. By this the grandmother registers the name of her blind grandson in city hospital to give sight to his blind eyes. As soon as the foot hospitalist called, and the child underwent as ophthalmologist to treat the child with an ophthalmologist. Through the hard struggling however finally the child getting the sight and looks the light of the world.

synopsis: A boy named Siddharth is the hero of this film. His parents Jawara and Nagavva will be working in a Kodagu estate due to their money problem and they would leave Siddharth in Betadhapura village for his education purpose in Ganesh shasthris house who was a freedom fighter. Ganapathi shasthri taught Siddharth about our countries heritage, history and about our national flag. He taught Siddharth about a women who had lot of respect on our country Gundamma and had given all her wealth for freedom fighters and died. Siddharth knowing about Gundammas patriotism towards the country, he with his friends to respect her hoists flag on a day which was not a national festival day. Police officers consider this behaviour as against government and arrest Ganapthi shasthri for being the reason for Siddharths behaviour and take him to the court. When Siddharth got to know about this he goes to the court and argues with judge that hoisting flag in order to respect Gundammas patriotism on non-nation festival day is not a mistake and requests to change the rule. Even judges consider his argument and torches out this to government. This is the short story of this film.
